text:
exec clear
exec crosshairswitcher/switcher; medic

load_itempreset 0

alias "+MedicRadar" "Hud_MedicAutocallersThreshold 500"
alias "-MedicRadar" "Hud_MedicAutocallersThreshold 50"
bind "SHIFT" "+MedicRadar"

bind "F5" "load_itempreset 0; alias chargetext charge1; alias pop pop1; alias medigun medigun1; echo loading preset 1 (stock)"
bind "F6" "load_itempreset 1; alias chargetext charge2; alias pop pop2; alias medigun medigun2; echo loading preset 2 (quickfix)"
bind "F7" "load_itempreset 2; alias chargetext charge3; alias pop pop3; alias medigun medigun3; echo loading preset 3 (kritz)"
bind "F8" "load_itempreset 3; alias chargetext charge4; alias pop pop4; alias medigun medigun4; echo loading preset 4 (vaccinator)"

alias chargetext charge1

bind "mouse4" "chargetext"
alias charge1 "voicemenu 2 5; say_team  bercharge ready. "
alias charge2 "voicemenu 2 5; say_team ** Quickfix ready. **"
alias charge3 "voicemenu 2 5; say_team  Kritzkrieg ready. "
alias charge4 "voicemenu 2 5; say_team  Vaccinator ready. "

alias pop pop1
alias pop1 "say_team  bercharge popped. "
alias pop2 "say_team ** Quickfix popped. **"
alias pop3 "say_team  Kritzkrieg popped. "
alias pop4 ""
bind "mwheeldown" "pop"

alias medigun medigun1
alias medigun1 "say_team  Stock medigun equipped."
alias medigun2 "say_team * Quickfix equipped."
alias medigun3 "say_team  Kritzkrieg equipped."
alias medigun4 "say_team  Vaccinator equipped."
bind "mwheelup" "medigun"

bind "t" "say Nobody SAW that coming!"
